        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for birthday greetings.</p>
            <p>Comments on work at Naples Zoological Station. F. M. Balfour to visit Naples. Would like to send third son [Francis Darwin] to learn art of observing marine animals.</p>
            <p>Health indifferent.</p>
